<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8">
        <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge,chrome=1">
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.9">
        <title>Open Teaching Project - 主页</title>
        <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/css/font-awesome/css/all.min.css">
        <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/css/bootstrap.min.css">
        <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/css/ui.css">
    </head>
    <body>
        <nav class="navbar navbar-dark bg-dark navbar-fixed-top">
            <a class="navbar-brand" href="/">Open Teaching Project</a>
            <% if (user) { %>
                <div class="justify-content-end">
                    <ul class="navbar-nav mr-auto">
                        <li class="nav-item" style="color:#fff;font-weight:bold;"><a href="/trust/settings/profile">欢迎！<%= user.name %></a></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            <% } else { %>
                <form class="form-inline">
                    <div class="input-group">
                        <input type="text" class="form-control mr-1">
                    </div>
                    <div class="input-group">
                        <input type="password" class="form-control mr-1">
                    </div>
                    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-success">Sign in</button>
                </form>
            <% } %>
        </nav>
        <!-- Main jumbotron for a primary marketing message or call to action -->
        <div class="jumbotron">
            <div class="container">
                <h1>欢迎来到OpenTeaching!</h1>
                <p>OpenTeaching是一个用于在线授课的开放平台，如果您是教师，可以在这里创建和管理自己的课堂并且在线给学生授课，如果您是学生，可以在这里加入自己感兴趣的课堂进行学习。</p>
                <p><a class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" href="#" role="button">了解更多 »</a></p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="container">	
            <div class="row" id="room-grid-view">
            </div>
            <div class="row">
                <video id="webcam"></video>
            </div>
        </div>
        <script src="/js/jquery.min.js"></script>
        <script src="/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
        <script src="/js/landing.js"></script>
        <script>
            $(document).ready(function(){
                landing.landing_setup ();
            });
        </script>
    </body>
</html>